text: Nikolayevka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Alataninsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 66 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Sterlitamak, 4 km from Alatana. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Nikolayevka, Alataninsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
